Package: decontam
Type: Package
Title: Identify Contaminants in Marker-gene and Metagenomics Sequencing Data
Version: 0.1.6
Author: Benjamin Callahan <benjamin.j.callahan@gmail.com>, Nicole Marie Davis
Maintainer: Benjamin Callahan <benjamin.j.callahan@gmail.com>
Description: Simple statistical identification of contaminating sequence features from 
    marker-gene or metagenomics data. Any kind of feature derived from the sequence data. 
    Requires DNA quantitation data or sequenced negative control samples.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1),
    methods (>= 3.3.1)
Imports:
    ggplot2 (>= 2.1.0),
    reshape2 (>= 1.4.1)
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
